"{\"uid\": \"standard.co.uk-sport-sport-olympics-when-is-sky-brown-competing-olympics-2024-skateboarding-start-time-tv-b1174875.html\", \"text\": \"To use the search feature, we need your consent to load Google Custom Search, which may use cookies or similar technologies. Please click 'Allow and Continue' below to enable search. See our privacy policy for more information.  Sport|Olympics  Sky Brownkicks off herOlympicscampaign atParis 2024as she competes in the women's park skateboarding tomorrow.  The teenager won a bronze medal in Tokyo, making herTeam GB's youngest ever medallist, and she now looks to make a return to the podium despite a recent injury scare.  Brown revealed that she suffered a dislocated shoulder the day before she travelled to Paris, admitting it was \\\"really scary\\\" as she feared for her participation at the Olympics.  The 16-year-old is set to have surgery when she returns home after the Games, but for now will rely on heavy strapping to minimise the pain.  Sky Brown will compete in the women's park skateboarding heats, which are scheduled to start at 11:30am BST on Tuesday, August 6. Brown is set to go in heat four.  She will hope to book her place in the final, which will take place at 4:30pm later in the day.  TV channel:In the UK, the women's park will be shown on BBC and Eurosport.  Live stream: Subscribers can visit the discovery+ | Paris 2024 app and website to watch the fight in full, while BBC's coverage schedule has not yet been confirmed.  Live blog: Follow live coverage of the fight withStandard Sport's rolling Olympics blog, with expert analysis from reporters Matt Majendie and Malik Ouzia in Paris.  MORE ABOUT  Have your say...  1  Crime  Fight breaks out on Elizabeth line train after youths told to stop vaping by middle-aged passenger  Fight breaks out on Elizabeth line after youths told to stop vaping  2  Football  Liverpool XI vs Brighton: Starting lineup, confirmed team news, injury latest for Premier League today  Liverpool XI vs Brighton: Starting lineup and confirmed team news  3  UK  Flights alert: UK issues global travel disruption warning over Donald Trump's Iran war  Flights alert: UK issues global travel disruption warning on Iran war  4  Lifestyle  Horoscope today: Your daily guide for Saturday, March 21, 2026  Horoscope today: Your daily guide for Saturday, March 21, 2026  5  Football  Arsenal XI vs Man City: Confirmed team news, predicted lineup, injury latest for Carabao Cup final  Arsenal XI vs Man City: Confirmed team news and predicted lineup\"}"